## Sprint Plan

### Sprint 1 — Backend + APIM gateway *(blocked on WI-7 deploy)*

| # | Task | Owner | Status | DoD |
|---|------|-------|--------|-----|
| WI-0 | `GET /v1/scrum/dashboard` endpoint + Cosmos cache in `33-eva-brain-v2` | brain team | 🔲 file created, needs deploy | Endpoint returns shaped ADO data; Cosmos `scrum-cache` TTL=24 h; unit tests pass |
| WI-1 | APIM route registration for `/v1/scrum/dashboard` + `/v1/scrum/summary` | apim team | 🔲 blocked on WI-7 | Routes live in `marco-sandbox-apim`; OAuth enforced; smoke test HTTP 200 |

**Blockers:**
- WI-7 (eva-brain deployed to sandbox) must be `Closed` before WI-0 endpoint can be tested against live Cosmos
- Cosmos container `scrum-cache` needs to be created in sandbox with partition key `/sprint_key` and TTL enabled

**Cosmos setup (one-time, manual until IaC):**
```bash
# In azure portal or via az cli:
az cosmosdb sql container create \
  --account-name <cosmos-account> \
  --database-name eva-foundation \
  --name scrum-cache \
  --partition-key-path /sprint_key \
  --default-ttl 86400
```

